snippet.title: Why is dividing by a fraction the same as multiplying by the reciprocal? (TANTON Mathematics)
snippet.description: Is it at all obvious that dividing by 4/7 is the same as multiplying by 7/4? We are all told to do this. Is it true? Let's find out!
